content:
Create Service Resources for Agents

Service resources represent individual agents. Create a service resource for each agent.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
To create service resources: "Create" on service resources

Open the Service Resources tab.
Click New.
For Name, enter the name of the agent.
Select the Active checkbox.
For User, use the lookup icon to select the agent.
For Resource Type, select Agent.
Click Save.
title: Service Resources for Agents
